OL,3,CChild cruelty and neglect risen by 76%
OL,4,Cin Kent in last decade, NSPCC figures
OL,5,Cshow
OL,7,FCases of child cruelty and neglect in
OL,8,FKent have risen by 76% in ten years,
OL,9,Faccording to the NSPCC. There were 386
OL,10,Frecorded offences between 2021-22,
OL,11,Fwhich rose to 792 in the next 12
OL,12,Fmonths, between 2022-23.
OL,14,FAcross the South East, child cruelty
OL,15,Fand neglect offences are up by a third
OL,16,Fin five years.
OL,18,FCases reported to police forces in
OL,19,FKent, Sussex and Surrey of children
OL,20,Fbeing subjected to cruelty or neglect
OL,21,Fhave risen by 33%.
